Task: GlYix0-small-fixes-aug13
==============================================================================

Goals
--------


During development of other features a number of small bug fixes and improvements were surfaced.
This set of small mostly unrelated changes are batched together to aid review.

1: Provide better error checking on pystache parsing errors.
2: 8-byte align ARM stacks.
3: Fix ARM reset constant.
4: Support for templated assembler modules.

